title: d3dx9_39_dll
body: hey I just got this new computer, i downloaded league, tried to run it but it says I am missing d3dx9_39_dll, how can I solve that issue?

replies.body:
You should be able to resolve this by running windows update, ensuring your graphics card has the [newest driver installed](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752684-Low-Frame-Rate-FPS-Troubleshooting#wq1), and installing the Directx 9 package [here.](https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=34429)

Let me know if this helped.
